Title:		brasero.tcz
Description:	CD/DVD Burning Application of GNOME.
Version:	2.32.1
Author:		Philippe Rouquier
Original-site:	http://live.gnome.org/Brasero
Copying-policy:	GPL-2
Size:		1.3M
Extension_by:	Arslan S.
Comments:	Optional dependencies:
			-cdrdao     : to burn CD-Rs at DAO mode (Disk-At-Once)
			-dvdauthor  : to create video DVDs
			-vcdimager  : to create VCDs and SVCDs
			-libdvdcss  : to copy encrypted DVDs
			-gst-plugins-bad or
			-gst-plugins-ugly or
			-gst-plugins-good or
			-gst-ffmpeg : for more audio and video format support when creating AUDIO CDs, DVD Movies, VCDs and SVCDs
			-libburn    : alternative burning backend
			-libisofs   : alternative iso backend

		This extension is PPI compatible.
